DND DM WISHLIST

1) MOVEMENT TRACKING
     • Where IS everyone?
     • Can I get there?
     • Melee or ranged attack?

2) TERRAIN
     • What IS there?
     • What can characters interact with/need to keep in mind?
     • Is a character covered? How much?

3) Conditions
     • Is an enemy dead, prone, etc?

4) Size
     • You versus Enemy, for perspective
